    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/cf7af78519a6f48c9c602ace01f114ab.avif?t=1717412892\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>Inspired by racing game giants like &quot;F-Zero&quot; and &quot;Wipeout,&quot; Unlimited offers a different take on high-speed racing, adding a level of freedom. Your performance isn't the only thing that matters—get creative!<br><br>Here, you can take off, skip parts of the track, and showcase your piloting skills to gain valuable seconds. However, to keep the challenge alive, your boost is directly fueled by the road. Without it, you won't get far.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/06213d5e9d264d2f71d327cc0d633790.poster.avif?t=1717412892\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/06213d5e9d264d2f71d327cc0d633790.webm?t=1717412892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/06213d5e9d264d2f71d327cc0d633790.mp4?t=1717412892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your Feedback is Valuable</strong></h2><strong>I'm very interested in your feedback and comments.</strong> Join the Discord server to share your thoughts and suggestions, which could have a significant impact on future development stages. Stay informed about upcoming features and additions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><strong>Fly!</strong><br>Unlimited is a racing game where speed and flight coexist. Get creative! You can literally fly off the track.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/db50fe10f76678d12c190f501dfc7a9b.poster.avif?t=1717412892\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/db50fe10f76678d12c190f501dfc7a9b.webm?t=1717412892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/db50fe10f76678d12c190f501dfc7a9b.mp4?t=1717412892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Realistic and Demanding Piloting</strong><br>This is not an arcade racing game! Unlimited's physics are designed for realistic handling. The ship has substantial inertia, and its maneuverability can become particularly complex at higher speeds.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/58322c0dee99f663ab93957b5491b143.poster.avif?t=1717412892\" width=600 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/58322c0dee99f663ab93957b5491b143.webm?t=1717412892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/58322c0dee99f663ab93957b5491b143.mp4?t=1717412892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Boost Management</strong><br>The boost system encourages you to go faster and faster. The more you accelerate, the more boost you gain, thereby increasing both speed and piloting difficulty.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/9823918ff718ac4141d0f70e0e74ab80.avif?t=1717412892\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br><br><strong>Challenge Your Friends and the Community!</strong><br>Play with up to 12 players in a match, against AI or online players. Your best times will be saved, allowing you to compete with your friends.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/2e21d7fc472387745c38626e0c8820c4.poster.avif?t=1717412892\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/2e21d7fc472387745c38626e0c8820c4.webm?t=1717412892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270720/extras/2e21d7fc472387745c38626e0c8820c4.mp4?t=1717412892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Future Development Stages</strong></h2>The game is currently in development, with an Early Access release planned for mid-2024. You can expect gameplay adjustments, as well as the addition of new maps and universes.<br><br>Don't forget to add Unlimited to your wishlist and come share your ideas on Discord. Your contribution matters a lot!",
